title: Did a European scientific journal conclude that September 11 was a controlled destruction?
subtitle: The viral news mispublished an article written by "9/11 Truth" advocates as an article published in the European Science Journal; it has already been published in the Eurovisal News, which is not peer-reviewed.
author: Alex Kasprak
vclaim: The European Scientific Journal, a peer-reviewed academic publication, concluded that the collapse of the twin towers and World Trade Centre 7 on 11 September 2001 was the result of controlled demolition.
